{"tid":1313650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"｛突發｝港大研究生會已取消14/7週年大會","createTime":"2019-07-14T00:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T05:39:58.000Z","uid":131731,"like":138,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1560a2367e633811afcc2da2346f2d46eb4a60","tid":1313650,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:10:18.000Z","msg":"各位同學：<br />\n <br />\n近日，我們關注到有關我會週年大會和修改會章的討論愈演愈烈，支持與反對的聲音愈發極端。為避免衝突升級，加劇研究生群體內部撕裂，我們決定取消原定今天下午2點於研究生堂王賡武講堂舉行的週年大會。<br />\n對於未能如期舉行週年大會我們向廣大會員表示道歉。同時我們<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>決定撤回此版會章修改草案並無限期接受會員提出的修改意見</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n**********************************************************************************************************************************************<br />\nDear students,<br />\n <br />\nThese days, we noticed the discussion on our Annual General Meeting and Constitution Amendment intensified, and the voices of both for and against are getting extreme. In order to avoid escalation of the conflict and the risk of tearing the postgraduate student community, we decided to cancel the Annual General Meeting to be held at Wang Gungwu Theatre, Graduate House, at 2:00 PM today.<br />\nWe deeply apologize for not being able to hold the AGM as scheduled. Also, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">we agree to retreat the Draft Constitution and indefinitely accept advice to the amendment of the Constitution</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\nPostgraduate Student Association<br />\nTHE UNIVERSITY OF HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n直接出沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798ca85527d1d59c5172097320a4e0d07a3bb135","tid":1313650,"uid":131731,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb69a75943e4912feee99f647170dd738d3e6ef","tid":1313650,"uid":33352,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:14:24.000Z","msg":"撒回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c310c01f58a1116c8edad48e13aec14c6b665c","tid":1313650,"uid":24875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"798ca85527d1d59c5172097320a4e0d07a3bb135","tid":1313650,"uid":131731,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:15:46.000Z","msg":"我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2555d714edcbbff605a91fe96efbd73bbb1b60","tid":1313650,"uid":131731,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"預咗要返hku嘅轉戰沙田啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ae900ab6a042cda7f881c816fdc6da0ea4d003","tid":1313650,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6175f85a6ccc5186afed459c054c189e4743380","tid":1313650,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"915cca1bf39719464d49f1e3c6ffd308c07168dd","tid":1313650,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:20:28.000Z","msg":"巴打們準備起床去沙田遊行未啊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313584</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0f1a73d9d651a7571b8aef9efaa3af04e91df18","tid":1313650,"uid":128923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy